b is a dangerous job.</strong> There is some residential work that any do-it-yourself-er can handle, but I would encourage you to hire a qualified electrician for this project.</li>\n</ol>', 'Electrical for hot tubs: Things to consider', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '62-autosave', '', '', '2012-02-28 19:56:43', '2012-02-28 19:56:43', '', '62', 'http://eazyelectric.com/62-autosave/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('112', '1', '2011-02-12 20:50:17', '2011-02-12 20:50:17', 'There are a few things to consider when you purchase a hot tub.  You must have { this kind of panel }, you must pull a permit and get it inspected.  Either you as the home owner can pull the permit { here - provide link }, or you can hire us to take care of the details.', 'Hot Tub Hookup', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '62-revision-2', '', '', '2011-02-12 20:50:17', '2011-02-12 20:50:17', '', '62', 'http://eazyelectric.com/62-revision-2/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('114', '1', '2011-02-13 04:13:04', '2011-02-13 04:13:04', 'GUARANTEED LOWEST PRICE!!!  WE\'LL BEAT ANY WRITTEN OFFER!!<a href=\"http://eazyelectric.dev/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/istockphoto_5487266-gesturing-retro-mustache-man-1970-s-style.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-98\" title=\"istockphoto_5487266-gesturing-retro-mustache-man-1970-s-style\" src=\"http://eazyelectric.dev/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/istockphoto_5487266-gesturing-retro-mustache-man-1970-s-style.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"380\" height=\"253\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThese promises that are made by contractors are usually made in the hope that you will just trust them and not worry to look for a cheaper deal.  In the chance you do find a lower price and present it to them, I find that the contractors will install cheap products and use unskilled labor as a way to beat this lower price you have found. Our promise to you is that \"we will use the highest quality products, installed by well educated electricians, in a safe and craftsman like manner, and