 a low overhead we can offer the same high quality work that you\'d expect from a larger company and still save big on your investment.  Besides saving money you will also feel comfortable as you experience family friendly service with the same effort I put into ensuring my families safety and comfort.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-18', '', '', '2012-03-29 23:04:41', '2012-03-29 23:04:41', '', '2', 'http://www.eazyelectric.com/2-revision-18/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('211', '1', '2011-09-30 05:05:27', '2011-09-30 05:05:27', 'Phone:\r\n(360) 620-8829\r\n\r\nMail:\r\nP.O. Box 25353\r\nSeattle, WA 98165', 'Contact Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '152-revision-5', '', '', '2011-09-30 05:05:27', '2011-09-30 05:05:27', '', '152', 'http://www.eazyelectric.com/152-revision-5/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('212', '1', '2011-09-13 22:34:34', '2011-09-13 22:34:34', 'GUARANTEED LOWEST PRICE!!!  WE\'LL BEAT ANY WRITTEN OFFER!!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-113 alignright\" title=\"cheezy sales guy\" src=\"http://eazyelectric.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/iStock_000005487266XSmall.jpg\" alt=\"eazy electric won\'t do this to you\" width=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nThese promises that are made by contractors are usually made in the hope that you will just trust them and not worry to look for a cheaper deal.  In the chance you do find a lower price and present it to them, I find that the contractors will install cheap products, which will only last long enough to get past the warranty, then you\'ll be calling someone to repair the faulty equipment.  These same contractors will also use unlicensed help which leaves your family and property in harms way. Our promise to you is that \"we will use the highest quality products, installed by well educated electricians, in a safe and craftsman like manner, and at a competitive rate.\"\r\n\r\nEazy Electric has a low overhead that allows for our prices to be lower without compromising the quality of ou